text.section:
The owner shall register each affected property using forms prepared by the Department, including the following information:
The name and address of the owner;
The address of the affected property;
If applicable, the name and address of each property manager employed by the owner to manage the affected property;
The name and address of each insurance company providing property insurance or lead hazard coverage for the affected property, together with the policy numbers of that insurance or coverage;
The name and address of a resident agent, other agent of the owner, or contact person in the State with respect to the affected property;
Whether the affected property was built before 1950 or after 1949;
The date of the latest change in occupancy of the affected property;
The dates and nature of treatments performed to attain or maintain a risk reduction standard under § 6-815 or § 6-819 of this subtitle; and
The latest date, if any, on which the affected property has been certified to be in compliance with the provisions of § 6-815 of this subtitle.
